<div class='container'>
  <div class='row'>
    <div class="col-md-12">
      <div class='row justify-content-center pt-md-5'>
        <h2><strong>本当に退会をさせますか？</strong></h2><br>
      </div>
      <div class='row justify-content-center pt-md-3'>
        <h4>退会処理を行うとこのアカウントは再利用できなくなります。</h4>
      </div>
      <div class='row justify-content-center pt-md-3'>
        <div class='form-group'>
          <%= form_with  url: admin_withdraw_path, method: :patch, local: true do |f| %>
            <%= f.hidden_field :id, value: @user.id %>
            <%= f.submit "退会", class: "btn btn-primary" %>
          <% end %>
        </div>
        <div class='form-group pl-md-3'>
          <%= link_to "退会しない", admin_user_path(@user.id),class: "btn btn-danger" %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
